        "title": "Q3-TLE8-FCS-LAS01-CONCEPTUALIZING BEAUTY CARE AND WELLNESS.pdf",
        "sourcePage": "https://sites.google.com/deped.gov.ph/deped-lrportal/dlp-materials/dlp-grade-8/quarter-3",
